00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:51,260
Just think of him as a walking money bag, and you'll be done with it after emptying it out.

508
00:38:51,260 --> 00:38:54,500
Su Wei'an, if you keep going on like this, I'll suspect that you still have feelings for Dr. Gu.

